Our social media pages and apps that we control (collectively, our “Social Media Pages”);
HTML-formatted email messages that we send to you that link to this Statement or other communications with you; and
Offline interactions you have with us.
Collectively, we refer to the Sites, Apps, Social Media Pages, emails, and offline  interactions as the “Services.”
The purpose of this Statement is to explain our global data practices. Please see our
United States Consumer Privacy Statement
for information regarding our United States personal data practices specifically. Please see our
Global Cookie Privacy Statement
for information regarding personal data collected automatically, including through cookies and other tracking technologies.
