This United States Consumer Privacy Statement (the “Statement”) describes how Chevron Corporation and its wholly owned subsidiaries (collectively, “Chevron,” “we,” or “us”)  collect, use, and disclose personal data relating to United States residents, including when they use our US websites (the “Sites”), mobile applications (the “Apps”), social media pages, emails, texts, and other offline business interactions (collectively, the “Services”). For purposes of this Statement, “personal data” is information that identifies you as an individual or relates to an identifiable individual.
This Statement does not address our data practices regarding the personal data of current or former employees, job applicants, contractors, or similar individuals.
For residents of certain states, this Statement also includes the
state-specific notice
appended to this Statement.
The following chart details the categories of personal data we collect and process, as well as the categories of personal data we disclose to third parties for our business purposes, including within the 12 months preceding the date this Statement was last updated. We may combine personal data that we receive about you, from you, and the sources described in this Statement for any of the business purposes described in this Statement.
We disclose personal data in certain instances for our marketing purposes. For example, we may engage third parties to help us deliver interest-based advertisements to you and may make use of third-party tracking technologies or other online marketing services.
These activities may be considered targeted advertising or “sharing” for purposes of cross-contextual behavioral advertising under applicable state privacy law. The chart also details the categories of personal data that we “share” for purposes of cross-contextual behavioral or targeted advertising, including within the 12 months preceding the date this Statement was last updated.
We may also “sell” personal data, as defined under applicable state privacy law, as provided below.
