Sub-policy 1
https://www.chevron.com/privacy/global-cookie-statement:
skip to main content
Effective date:
December 13, 2024
This website, Chevron.com, is owned and operated in the United States. In this Global Cookie Privacy Statement (“Statement”), “we” means Chevron Corporation and its wholly owned subsidiaries, and “you” means the person interacting with us online, such as when you visit or use Chevron.com (the “Site”) or our United States-based Chevron, Texaco or ExtraMile Rewards consumer mobile applications (the “Apps,” collectively with the Site and other online interactions, the “Services”). “Cookie(s)” means cookies and similar tracking technologies described in further detail below.
This Statement describes the personal data practices of Chevron Corporation, its wholly owned subsidiaries (collectively, “Chevron,” “we,” or “us”) and the ExtraMile App in connection with personal data collected through the use of Cookies. The purpose of this Statement is to explain our online tracking practices more fully and how you may control them. Please see our
United States Consumer Privacy Statement
for information regarding our United States data practices generally (including personal data collected through the Site or the Apps) and our
Global Privacy Statement
for more general information regarding our personal data practices globally, including through the Site or the Apps.
The Site uses the following types of Cookies. Please also see our
Cookie Settings
for more information about certain types of Cookies.
