Through Checking Pay, Pay With Spire, Inc., (“Spire”, “we” or “us”), provides access to services (collectively, the “Services”) that allow you to use Checking Pay as a method of payment (“Payment”) at any retail locations operating under the Chevron® or Texaco® brands (collectively, “Branded Locations”). In this Terms of Service, “Customer”, “user” or “you” means any person using the Service.
This agreement (“Agreement”) sets forth the terms and conditions that apply to the use of this website and/or mobile application on which Spire provides the Service to you. READ THIS AGREEMENT CAREFULLY. If you do not agree to these terms and conditions, you may not use Checking Pay. Void where prohibited. Neither Apple, Inc. (App Store), Google, Inc. (Google Play), nor any other app store or marketplace is responsible for the Services or any contents.
