By using this website or application (other than to read this agreement for the first time), by indicating acceptance of this agreement, by using Checking Pay, by signing up for Checking Pay, or otherwise using the services, you are entering into this agreement with Spire and agree to comply with these terms and conditions and our privacy policy, available at
